lead_paragraph: The introduction of Formula One's new qualifying system will be delayed until the fifth race of the season due to technical issues, the sport's commercial supremo Bernie Ecclestone said on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: New F1 Qualifying Faces Delayed Introduction
